   <refnamediv>
       <refname>a2q </refname>
               <refpurpose>expand an annual series into a quarterly one </refpurpose>
   </refnamediv>
 
        <refsynopsisdiv>
               <title>CALLING SEQUENCE</title>
               <synopsis>tsout=a2q(tsin)</synopsis>
        </refsynopsisdiv>
 
        <refsection>
           <title>PARAMETERS</title>
           <variablelist>
           <varlistentry>
 
           <term>Input</term>
 
<listitem><para>* <term> tsin</term> = an annual time series</para></listitem>
 
 
           </varlistentry>
 
          <varlistentry>
 
          <term>Output</term>
 
<listitem><para>* <term> tsout</term>  = the corresponding quarterly time series</para></listitem>
 
 
          </varlistentry>
          </variablelist>
        </refsection>
 
        <refsection>
               <title>DESCRIPTION</title>
Expands an annual series into a quarterly one, by duplicating 4 times the annual values. 

        </refsection>
 
        <refsection>
               <title>EXAMPLE</title>
              <programlisting role="example"><![CDATA[
x = reshape([1:35],'1978a') // ceate an annual ts
y = a2q(x) 
// gives an montly ts, from 1978q1 to 2012q4 with values 1 for all quarters of year 1978, 
// 2 for all quarters of year 1979...
 
               ]]></programlisting>
        </refsection>
 
        <refsection>
               <title>AUTHOR</title>
Eric Dubois 2020
        </refsection>
</refentry>
